						<summary>

						<p>On a stone built into the flooring of the Vīrabhadra temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 15th century.</p>						

						<p>The extant portion refers to Chaitra śu 10, all other details of date being lost.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record a gift of money to the god Sōmanātha. The inscription is damaged.</p>						

						</summary>
